{"tid":196605,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓市加辣 辣咩？】收緊一約多伙 多於一伙契約繳15%稅 午夜生效","createTime":"2017-04-11T12:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T13:17:58.000Z","uid":41367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"114c951c8a060e27d25cf73c63efd45ec19e47a4","tid":196605,"uid":41367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:09:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170411/56551322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170411%2F56551322&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi68KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=ab12b557\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170411%2F56551322&h=e7bfa67a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170411/56551322</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官梁振英，將聯同財政司司長陳茂波及運輸及房屋局局長張炳良，於7時15分見傳媒，推出新一輪樓市辣招，收緊一約多伙。<br />\n梁振英表示，政府處理房屋問題，除大力增加土地供應外，亦推出多項管理需求措施，包括限制外地人需求、投機及投資需求，令本地人買樓優先。但樓市仍受超低息環境影響。近期有買家以一約多伙形式入市，引起政府關注，令樓市氣氛轉趨熾熱。政府明日起，限制買家以一份文書購入多個單位，即以15%新稅率繳稅，今晚午夜起生效。<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波表示，未來3至4年，一手住宅物業樓花維持高水平，會超出9.4萬伙。過去5年，住宅物業落成量6萬伙，平均每年1.2萬伙，而未來5年是有10萬一千伙，平均每年2萬伙。市場的租盤及買賣盤有一定的影響。"},{"pid":"2d90c9ad9b7aa19b60f539d4cca7c665cbc7d375","tid":196605,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:11:23.000Z","msg":"零作用"},{"pid":"6abda9a2e8e0b7798cd0a32c5bcf0ffb127a1cb3","tid":196605,"uid":41367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T12:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f505c39f8cf788ecbd9cd873189148a69b2303a8","tid":196605,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"班狗官趕完尾班車 買完啦 ?   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}